        "date": "2026-04-29T18:01:46Z",
        "message": "Merge pull request #15 from qs2d/fix/mac-zero-pad\n\nfix: zero-pad MAC address hex bytes in Decode()",
        "url": "https://github.com/acheong08/apple-corelocation-experiments/commit/0b136860e80585c02c12f64933995b872d7623af"
